11:19.440 --> 11:20.668
Hey!

11:27.240 --> 11:28.514
You speaking Spanish, guera?

11:29.440 --> 11:33.752
[speaking Spanish]

11:33.880 --> 11:35.711
[man speaking Spanish]

11:35.840 --> 11:37.592
I-I don't understand.
I'm sorry.

11:37.680 --> 11:40.240
He say that it is hard
to paddle against the current.

11:40.320 --> 11:41.799
Yeah, I wasn't expecting that.

11:41.880 --> 11:44.348
I almost got caught
on the inside coming out.

11:44.440 --> 11:46.431
[speaking Spanish]

11:46.520 --> 11:47.520
- You American?
- Okay.

11:47.840 --> 11:49.558
Sí. Sí, American.

11:49.640 --> 11:50.709
Yeah!

11:50.800 --> 11:52.836
California?

11:52.920 --> 11:54.399
Uh, close.

11:54.480 --> 11:55.356
Texas.

11:55.440 --> 11:57.908
There's surf in Texas?

11:58.000 --> 11:59.433
Yes, we have surf in Texas.

11:59.520 --> 12:01.431
It's just not
like this, though.

12:01.520 --> 12:02.520
[speaks Spanish]

12:02.560 --> 12:03.834
[speaking Spanish]

12:03.920 --> 12:05.831
[laughter]

12:05.920 --> 12:07.399
[chuckles]

12:07.480 --> 12:09.232
Hey, this is a secret break.

12:09.320 --> 12:10.878
How you find it?

12:11.000 --> 12:12.991
Someone told me about it
a while ago.

12:13.080 --> 12:14.195
What's it called?

12:14.280 --> 12:15.508
If I tell you,

12:15.600 --> 12:17.750
I would have to kill you!

12:17.880 --> 12:19.552
Well, that would ruin my day.

12:19.640 --> 12:23.030
Anything gnarly out here,
I should know about?

12:23.120 --> 12:24.758
There's some rocks over there!

12:24.840 --> 12:26.831
There's only one tide a day,

12:26.920 --> 12:29.275
and when the tide gets low,
it becomes an island.

12:29.360 --> 12:31.669
There's some nasty fire coral.

12:31.760 --> 12:34.035
It stings like a jellyfish.

12:34.120 --> 12:35.792
Okay! Gracias.

12:35.880 --> 12:36.995
Sí... [speaking Spanish]

12:38.760 --> 12:40.398
Hey, guera...

12:40.480 --> 12:43.631
[speaking Spanish]

12:43.720 --> 12:47.030
Still have no idea
what you're saying.

12:47.160 --> 12:50.197
He's saying that you should
come over here.

12:50.280 --> 12:51.872
The wave breaks better.

12:52.000 --> 12:53.274
Oh, I'm okay, I'm okay.

12:53.360 --> 12:55.396
I'm cool here, thank you.

12:55.480 --> 12:57.152
Careful, gringa.

12:57.240 --> 13:00.630
It's rough out here
for a little girl from Texas.

13:00.720 --> 13:02.312
I think I'll be all right.

13:10.800 --> 13:14.315
iVámonos! iVámonos!

13:14.400 --> 13:16.834
[speaking Spanish]

13:24.800 --> 13:27.792
