16:10.920 --> 16:11.955
[phone chimes]

16:12.040 --> 16:13.040
- Short crop?
- Hey!

16:13.680 --> 16:14.908
- Guess where I am?
- Tijuana.

16:15.920 --> 16:17.831
[laughs]

16:17.920 --> 16:20.309
Oh, my God. No way.

16:20.400 --> 16:21.896
- Mom's beach, right?
- It's just as beautiful

16:21.920 --> 16:24.753
as she said it was.

16:24.840 --> 16:26.910
I wish you were here.

16:27.000 --> 16:28.274
I wish she was here.

16:28.360 --> 16:30.351
Does that mean you're alone?

16:30.440 --> 16:33.159
Well, I wasn't gonna come all
this way just to wuss out

16:33.240 --> 16:35.037
because I lost my plus one.

16:35.120 --> 16:37.634
That's how you wind up
on Nancy Grace, okay?

16:37.720 --> 16:39.233
Excuse me.

16:39.320 --> 16:41.416
I am supposed to be the boring,
overprotective sister.

16:41.440 --> 16:43.032
You are supposed
to be the fun one.

16:43.120 --> 16:45.793
Sis, the surf here,
it's insane.

16:45.880 --> 16:48.474
You would not believe
the perfect tube I just caught.

16:48.560 --> 16:50.391
I could shoot tubes
just as good as you,

16:50.480 --> 16:52.391
if you would just take me out!

16:52.480 --> 16:54.675
I'll take you. I'll take you out
as soon as I get back.

16:55.360 --> 16:57.316
I love you, sister-mama.

16:57.400 --> 16:59.480
- I love you, too, short crop.
- [man] Is that Nancy?

16:59.520 --> 17:01.256
- It's Dad.
- Just tell him it's all fine, okay?

17:01.280 --> 17:02.816
- Love you. Bye.
- Uh, no, it's, it's a friend.

17:02.840 --> 17:04.016
[Dad]
Hey, Nance, don't hang up.

17:04.040 --> 17:06.031
Give me the phone. Chloe.

17:06.119 --> 17:07.030
Hey!

17:07.119 --> 17:08.269
Hey, Papa.

17:08.359 --> 17:09.474
Hey, sweet pea.

17:09.560 --> 17:10.595
Where now?

17:10.680 --> 17:12.318
Mexico.

17:12.400 --> 17:14.038
I don't know
what to say, Nance.

17:14.119 --> 17:15.712
I'm at a loss.
[laughs]

17:15.800 --> 17:17.359
I don't, I don't,
I can't understand.

17:17.440 --> 17:19.510
- I don't expect you to.
- Well, help me out, then.

17:19.920 --> 17:21.695
I don't know. What do you, uh,
what do you want me to say?

17:21.720 --> 17:23.118
Oh, say you're coming back.

17:23.200 --> 17:24.872
Say you're not dropping
out of med school

17:24.960 --> 17:27.109
after all this time,
after all this work.

17:27.200 --> 17:28.816
- You know, just don't quit.
- Okay. Okay, Dad.

17:28.840 --> 17:30.637
That's enough. Can we just

17:30.720 --> 17:31.994
not do this right now, please?

17:32.080 --> 17:33.798
It's what you love.
You help people.

17:33.880 --> 17:35.472
Well, not everyone
can be helped, Dad.

17:35.560 --> 17:36.788
You-you know that.

17:36.880 --> 17:39.235
Don't do that.

17:39.320 --> 17:40.360
Don't make this about her.

17:40.440 --> 17:43.830
What else would it be about?

17:43.920 --> 17:47.276
If you want to make this
about her, then you stay in it.

17:47.360 --> 17:48.713
She was a fighter.

17:52.960 --> 17:55.633
It's just she fought
too hard, Dad.

17:55.760 --> 17:59.992
You know? And for what?

18:00.080 --> 18:02.992
It all ended the same.

18:03.080 --> 18:05.230
Just come back, Nancy.

18:05.320 --> 18:06.673
Please.

18:07.960 --> 18:08.960
I gotta go, okay?

18:09.000 --> 18:10.956
- I'll see you soon.
- When?

18:11.040 --> 18:12.678
- When?
- I don't know.

18:12.760 --> 18:14.273
Nance.

18:14.360 --> 18:15.998
I love you. Bye.

18:17.080 --> 18:19.799
[♪♪♪]

18:35.960 --> 18:37.871
[phone chimes]

18:39.120 --> 18:42.908
[♪♪♪]

18:57.600 --> 19:00.717
[seabirds calling]

19:15.240 --> 19:17.993
[slow, deep breathing]

19:32.480 --> 19:34.152
Yeah, girl, it's getting late.

19:34.240 --> 19:35.798
Let's go in.

19:35.880 --> 19:37.791
I'm gonna catch
one last one. Thanks.

19:37.880 --> 19:39.552
Okay.

19:39.640 --> 19:41.256
- Nice meeting you guys.
- See you later, guera!

19:41.280 --> 19:43.430
Buenas noches.

