Help... me!

26:06.480 --> 26:08.198
I'm here!

26:10.600 --> 26:12.397
I'm here!

26:12.480 --> 26:13.799
Help!

26:17.280 --> 26:18.793
Yes. Yeah.

26:18.880 --> 26:20.677
Here!

26:20.760 --> 26:22.352
Here! Here!

26:24.680 --> 26:26.750
